This is a Django ADHD task management application.

Code Standards:
- Follow Django best practices and PEP 8
- Use TDD - write tests first
- Apply SOLID principles
- Include comprehensive error handling
- Add proper logging for debugging
- Consider ADHD-specific accessibility needs

Django Preferences:
- Use class-based views with mixins
- Prefer Django REST framework for APIs
- Use factory_boy for test fixtures
- Include docstrings for all models and views
- Structure apps by feature, not by layer

Testing:
- Aim for 90%+ test coverage
- Test edge cases and error conditions
- Include integration tests for workflows
- Mock external services appropriately